ource src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115560/extras/b6f774de6cba655d7d8630e3c627c483.webm?t=1674693910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115560/extras/b6f774de6cba655d7d8630e3c627c483.mp4?t=1674693910\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Persevere</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Keep pushing forward every time you die. Your death is certaintly not the end, and so keep persevering towards the very end.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115560/extras/b52f8661c9da7b8a42ac236a39015bfc.poster.avif?t=1674693910\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115560/extras/b52f8661c9da7b8a42ac236a39015bfc.webm?t=1674693910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115560/extras/b52f8661c9da7b8a42ac236a39015bfc.mp4?t=1674693910\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Find your <strong>Freedom</strong>",
